abstracts.cdata!:
The project would provide assistance to
            the Government of Oman in improving its capacity to
            administer and manage its economy. The assistance comprises
            the provision of three specialist teams dealing with: (i)
            economic planning and management; (ii) agriculture; and
            (iii) transportation. Appropriate office accommodation,
            housing, vehicles, local support staff, facilities and
            office equipment would be provided by the Government.
